The hotel rooms are very clean and spacious.	All staff were very friendly and helpful.	The rooms were extremely clean and quiet.	The staff was very helpful and accommodating.	The hotel is fantastic!	Location is far away from the city.	Staff were very helpful and accomodating.	The beach near the hotel was very good and again away from the main areas.	Breakfast was included in the price of our room and was quite basic.	This hotel was a great place to stay in Barcelona.	The metro station is about a 5 minute walk and easy to use into town.